  "text": "The Duits-Guedens critical kernel for the two-matrix model was derived in [CITATION_1] , and our proof of Theorem 1.7 is based on the presentation in [CITATION_2] . The critical kernel is described in terms of the tacnode RHP with parameters [26, Formula (2.41)]",
